# Naming Conventions

Follow existing patterns in `src/lib/` and `src/components/`.

## Functions & variables

| Kind | Pattern | Examples |
|---|---|---|
| General | `camelCase` | `localePath`, `truncate`, `sendMail` |
| Async fetchers | `fetch` + domain | `fetchCollectionType`, `fetchABEvents` |
| Config getters | `get` + noun | `getNavConfig`, `getLocale` |
| URL builders | domain + `Url` | `strapiMediaUrl`, `mediaUrl` |
| Type guards | `is` + predicate | `isDropdown`, `isWasabiUrl` |
| Page-local formatters | short `fmt` prefix | `fmtDay`, `fmtTime` (`.astro` frontmatter only) |
| Booleans | `is` / `has` / `can` | `isGated`, `hasToken` |

Prefer `export function name()` over `export const name = () =>` for named helpers (except small one-liners like `truncate`).

## Types & interfaces

- `PascalCase`, no `I` prefix: `NavConfig`, `SIEvent`, `Locale`
- Discriminated union members: descriptive string literals (`'text-left'`, `'img-left'`)
- Config singletons: `camelCase` + `Config` suffix — `siConfig`, `abConfig`

## Components & files

| Asset | File name | Export |
|---|---|---|
| Astro component | `PascalCase.astro` | default (implicit) |
| React island | `PascalCase.tsx` | `export default function Name` |
| Page route | URL slug, kebab-case | `index.astro`, `[slug].astro`, `kampe.astro` |
| Lib module | `kebab-case.ts` or domain | `client.ts`, `nav-config.ts` |

Folder names: lowercase (`brand/`, `islands/`, `homepage/`).

## Constants

- Module-level immutable lists: `SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE` — `GATED_PATHS`
- Env-backed config objects: `camelCase` — `siConfig`
- UI string dictionaries: short name `t` in `@/lib/i18n` only

## API routes

Export HTTP verbs as named const: `GET`, `POST` with type `APIRoute`.

## Avoid

- Abbreviations outside established prefixes (`fetch`, `get`, `fmt`, `Url`)
- Generic names (`data`, `handleClick`) in shared lib code
- Duplicate `Locale` type — import from `@/lib/i18n`
